document_title: Stage II cervical cancer: Signs and treatment
subsection_content: Stage II cervical cancer is cancer that has begun to spread outside the cervix and invade surrounding tissues, but has not invaded the lower 1/3 of the vagina and pelvic wall.
subsection_title: ung thu co tu cung giai doan 2.json. What is stage II cervical cancer?
subsection_data:
ung thu co tu cung giai doan 2.json. What is stage II cervical cancer?
Stage II cervical cancer is cancer that has begun to spread outside the cervix and invade surrounding tissues, but has not invaded the lower 1/3 of the vagina and pelvic wall.
